The room is immense and seems to go on forever. Upon further inspection, the walls and ceiling seem to be covered in some reflective material. Through cracks in the ceiling, slits of sunlight bathe the floor in light. Upon a strange looking mound in the center of the room is a very reflective object.
#ROOM_STATE_1#

The walls and ceiling of the room are reflective. There is a strange circular hole in one of the walls. There is a discuss-shaped spot on the floor that you could potentially USE.

#ROOM_STATE_2#

After the discus is inserted into the slot, a portion of the floor shakes and gives way to reveal a ladder on the East side of the room.
